{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2378195, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "质量守恒，初中化学", "timestamp": 1630163302, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不可能", "timestamp": 1630163327, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378198, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可能，吃得太咸会水钠潴留（因为多吃盐所以身体多积攒了水）", "timestamp": 1630163329, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378200, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还喝水呼吸啊", "timestamp": 1630163332, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378218, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但是不是增加了，这种情况过几天就能把水盐代谢掉体重降一些", "timestamp": 1630163397, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378223, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378218, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 那不就是不可能", "timestamp": 1630163428, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378236, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378223, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 可能达成第一天吃了1kg第2天一称重了2kg", "timestamp": 1630163510, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378255, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378236, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 那多出来的1kg哪来的？直接从空气里吸水吗？", "timestamp": 1630163600, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378345, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378255, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 宁不喝水吗？宁就算不喝水身体里没有细胞内液细胞外液吗？肾脏能自动条件排钠排水，体液渗透压太高的时候多储水有什么问题吗？宁别抬杠说宁不尿或者尿多，少尿无尿或者尿崩那是有大病", "timestamp": 1630163943, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378348, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378255, "tag": null, "text": "*调节", "timestamp": 1630163954, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378377, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378255, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 最简单地说宁难道吃了咸的不会口渴？", "timestamp": 1630164106, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378380, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378348, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 喝水那不就是又摄入了质量吗？不喝水的话细胞内液细胞外液不是本来就是身体里的？管他在细胞内还是细胞外不都本来就算在体重了？", "timestamp": 1630164118, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378393, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378377, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 你吃了1kg盐，就只增重1kg。后来口渴了再喝1kg水，那就是吃了2kg东西，增重2kg。怎么盐就算吃进去的水就不算了？", "timestamp": 1630164172, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378395, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378380, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 笑死，是我大意了，我不知道宁看不出来我一开始说了半天水钠潴留这事竟然和喝水有关", "timestamp": 1630164190, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378402, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378393, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: cz只是想表达这不是严格意义上的体重增长，属于正常波动，不会稳定维持在高值", "timestamp": 1630164250, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378405, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378395, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: xs，我意思是喝水也该算进吃的东西里，不能像你这样单独把水摘出来。", "timestamp": 1630164258, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378417, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378393, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 树洞可太迷惑了本来好好在说话解释这都能被宁杠得又来有回，宁自己品鉴初中化学去吧，👋🏻", "timestamp": 1630164325, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378439, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": 2378402, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 真有意思，dz问“吃进去1kg体重可能增加2kg吗”，你非把过两天喝的水导致的增重归因于现在吃的1kg盐，还扯什么细胞内液外液，还要说我杠。", "timestamp": 1630164484, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2378448, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 454231, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "“只有一个人回复了一句，树洞评论可能增加两条吗？”“可能，因为这句话可能引起其他人的回复”", "timestamp": 1630164564, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 454231, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "长胖的重量可能大于吃进去东西的重量吗，也就是说吃进去1kg体重可能增加2kg吗", "timestamp": 1630163237, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1630164564, "url": "", "vote": {}}}